2026-05-08T01:06:05.0324476Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-08T01:06:05.0326288Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-08T01:06:05.0327067Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-08T01:06:05.0327844Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
